{
  "tracks": [
    {
      "artist": "Goo Goo Dolls",
      "title": "Iris",
      "popups": [
        {
          "timeMs": 7000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "This song was written for the film 'City of Angels' starring Meg Ryan and Nicolas Cage.",
          "image": "popup_images/popcorn.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 14000,
          "durationMs": 6000,
          "text": "The band's performance scenes were shot in the same tunnel used in the movie.",
          "image": "popup_images/movie_camera.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 21000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "In \"the city of angels\"",
          "image": "popup_images/globe.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 26000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Los Angeles is Spanish for \"the angels\" - it is an abbreviation of the city's original name...",
          "image": "popup_images/open_book.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 30500,
          "durationMs": 7000,
          "text": "El Pueblo de Nuestra Senora La Reina de Los Angeles de Porciuncla",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 39000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Meg Ryan's original name: Margaret Mary Emily Anne Hyra",
          "image": "popup_images/chatting_silhouettes.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 44000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "His name: John Rzeznick",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 50000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "John started writing songs while studying plumbing at a vocational school in Buffalo, NY.",
          "image": "popup_images/nose.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 58000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "He gave up plumbing and formed the Goo Goo Dolls in 1985...",
          "image": "popup_images/guitar.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 63000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "At Buffalo State University - 299 miles north of Flushing, NY",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 71000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "The concept: John is an \"agorophobic man watching the world\" from his tower",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 77000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "agorophobia (n.): the fear of big crowds and public places",
          "image": "popup_images/open_book.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 83000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "Nicolas Cage suffered from acrophobia on the set of City of Angels - he is afraid of heights",
          "image": "popup_images/crying_face.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 94000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "John didn't suffer from acrophobia in this \"tower\" - it was built on a soundstage.",
          "image": "popup_images/smiling_face.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 100000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "The crew also built most of the telescopes on this set.",
          "image": "popup_images/drill.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 106000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "The director described this shoot as \"charmed\" - except for a problem with the telescopes.",
          "image": "popup_images/magnifying_glass.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 112000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "They kept breaking!",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 118000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Nicolas Cage took the last name Cage because he didn't want people to know who he is:",
          "image": "popup_images/chatting_silhouettes.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 124000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Nicolas Coppola - nephew of director Francis Ford Coppola!",
          "image": "popup_images/exclmation.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 129500,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "John has said he was drunk when he came up with the band's \"stupid name.\"",
          "image": "popup_images/martini_glass.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 136000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "He was reading a comic book in a bar and came across an ad for a \"spooky toy\":",
          "image": "popup_images/witch.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 141200,
          "durationMs": 6000,
          "text": "A Goo Goo Dall is a finger puppet of a baby's head.",
          "image": "popup_images/baby_doll_head.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 149000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Toy makers introduced the first baby doll that ate and dirtied her diapers in 1972.",
          "image": "popup_images/quill_paper.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 166000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "John had already written this song when he named it after L.A. club singer Iris Dement.",
          "image": "popup_images/microphone.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 171000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "He doesn't know Iris - he just thought she had \"a cool name.\"",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 178000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Gazing directly at stars through a telescope can damage the eye's retina - but not the iris.",
          "image": "popup_images/exclamation.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 183000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "It can also cause tunnel vision  ;)",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 189000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "What is one by-product of all eye infections?",
          "image": "popup_images/question_mark.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 196000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Too much goo-goo",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 201000,
          "durationMs": 6000,
          "text": "The film company made John re-record \"Iris\" without the band for the film's score.  The Goo Goos didn't boo-hoo, but they \"delibertly wasted\" the company's money!",
          "position": "TOP_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 208000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "John spent two days in the studio drinking champagne and \"screwing up on purpose.\"",
          "position": "TOP_CENTER"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "artist": "Lisa Loeb",
      "title": "Stay (I Missed You)",
      "popups": [
        {
          "timeMs": 5000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Ethan Hawke's cat",
          "image": "popup_images/down_arrow.webp",
          "position": "TOP_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 15000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Shot in a vacant Soho loft in NYC over 14 hours in March 1994",
          "image": "popup_images/globe.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 22000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Lisa Anne Loeb\nBorn: Bethesda, MD\nDate: March 11, 1968",
          "image": "popup_images/birthday_cake.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 34000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "This was Ethan Hawke's first time as a director.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 41000,
          "durationMs": 6000,
          "text": "It was Lisa's first time in front of the camera.",
          "image": "popup_images/movie_camera.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 53000,
          "durationMs": 6000,
          "text": "The idea - she's talking to a boyfriend leaving her alone in an empty apartment.",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 60000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "The video’s stripped-down apartment setting helped make it one of the most recognizable low-key videos of the '90s.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 67000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "There was a crew of 40 in the apartment that day - squashed against a back wall.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 74000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Hawke plotted the camera moves on the back of a greasy placement during the shoot.",
          "image": "popup_images/movie_camera.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 80000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "He and Lisa both deny rumors they were ever involved.",
          "image": "popup_images/heart_locket.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 86000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Hawks prey on smaller birds.",
          "image": "popup_images/exclamation.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 86000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "They can maneuver rapidly among trees!",
          "image": "popup_images/exclamation.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 98000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Lisa says her look is \"natural - not trendy.\"",
          "image": "popup_images/fashion_dummy.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 108000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Lisa is allergic to contact lenses.",
          "image": "popup_images/first_aid_bag.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 115000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "People \"allergic\" to contact with others are called \"haptephobic\".",
          "image": "popup_images/open_book.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 122000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Lisa grew up in Texas and speaks fluent Spanish.",
          "image": "popup_images/book_with_key.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 129000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "El gato de Ethan Hawke",
          "image": "popup_images/down_arrow.webp",
          "position": "TOP_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 153000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Most dogs can be taught to \"stay\" within 2 weeks.",
          "image": "popup_images/exclamation.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 159000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "60% of people won't stay with their current partner.",
          "image": "popup_images/broken_heart.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 165000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Scenes with Lisa's band \"Nine Stories\" were filmed.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 170000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "... But not used!",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "artist": "Alanis Morissette",
      "title": "You Learn",
      "popups": [
        {
          "timeMs": 5000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Pictures on the wall - Thrift shop: $2 each",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 13000,
          "durationMs": 6000,
          "text": "Alanis Morissette\nBorn: June 1, 1974\nPlace: Ottawa, Canada\nSign: Gemini",
          "image": "popup_images/birthday_cake.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 21000,
          "durationMs": 8000,
          "text": "Jacket - Thrift shop, vintage 1970s",
          "image": "popup_images/fashion_dummy.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 37000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Tetanus shots are recommended every 10 yrs.",
          "image": "popup_images/first_aid_bag.webp",
          "position": "TOP_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 45000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Single shot from a 35 ft crane.",
          "image": "popup_images/movie_camera.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 52500,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "There were 240 pedestrian fatalities in NYC in 1994.",
          "image": "popup_images/exclamation.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 57000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "There were no arrests for jaywalking.",
          "image": "popup_images/justice.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 63000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Alanis is named after her father, Alan, a high school principal.",
          "image": "popup_images/family.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 70000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "She has a twin brother named Wade.",
          "image": "popup_images/family.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 77000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "It's against NYFD regulations for firefighters to wear blue jeans.",
          "image": "popup_images/justice.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 86000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Name: Dolly\nAge: 10\nCost: $100/hr",
          "image": "popup_images/handprint.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 95000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "The crew used carrots to coax Dolly into the gym.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 102000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "Warm-up jacket #2",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 107000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Canada's Women's Basketball team finished 11th out of 12 teams in the 1996 Olympics.",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 114000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "Alanis sank this basket in one take.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 121000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "15 year-old gymnast wearing a wig.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "TOP_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 126000,
          "durationMs": 2000,
          "text": "Jacket #3",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 129000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "As a girl, Alanis idolized Olivia Newton-John in the movie \"Grease.\"",
          "image": "popup_images/book_with_key.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 132100,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "She wrote her first song at age 9.",
          "image": "popup_images/book_with_key.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 140000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "A peck uses 20 muscles. A \"French\" kiss uses 40.",
          "image": "popup_images/first_aid_bag.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 144100,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "Jacket #4",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 149000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "NYC Sanitation Dept - 13,000 tons of trash collected a day.",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 155000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "\"Dreadlocks\" took 5 hours to create.",
          "image": "popup_images/spiky_hair.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 166000,
          "durationMs": 3400,
          "text": "Her hair is bunched together with invisible thread.",
          "image": "popup_images/spiky_hair.webp",
          "position": "TOP_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 171000,
          "durationMs": 2400,
          "text": "10 ft jump",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 175100,
          "durationMs": 2000,
          "text": "Jacket #5",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 179000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "Tyler Hawkins: Drummer",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 182100,
          "durationMs": 2500,
          "text": "Whipped cream",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 186100,
          "durationMs": 2500,
          "text": "Band members",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 191000,
          "durationMs": 2500,
          "text": "Jacket #6",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 199000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Casting director cast herself as the opponent",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 213000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "The average women's boxing match lasts 3 rounds.",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 218000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "\"We live and learn, but not the wiser grow.\" John Pomfret 1667-1702",
          "image": "popup_images/open_book.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 224000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "This video was shot on February 11, 1996 in New York's meat packing district.  Filming took 23 hours in 10 degree weather.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "TOP_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 230000,
          "durationMs": 8000,
          "text": "Alanis performed the night before in Boston, drove all night, then slept in her tour bus parked outside the location.  She kept all six jackets.",
          "image": "popup_images/clapperboard.webp",
          "position": "TOP_CENTER"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "artist": "R.E.M.",
      "title": "Shiny Happy People",
      "popups": [
        {
          "timeMs": 24500,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "Michael Stipe of R.E.M.",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 28000,
          "durationMs": 3000,
          "text": "Kate Pierson of the B-52's",
          "image": "popup_images/up_arrow.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_RIGHT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 32000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Filmed in Athens, GA - hometown of both R.E.M. and the B-52's",
          "image": "popup_images/globe.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 38000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "The director wanted this video to be \"colorful and joyful - with no trace of irony or cynicism.\"",
          "image": "popup_images/light_bulb.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 44000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "Michael picked out his own yellow suit for the video.",
          "image": "popup_images/blue_head.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 50000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "He insisted on wearing one thing that made him feel particularly \"happy\".",
          "image": "popup_images/smiling_face.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 59000,
          "durationMs": 4500,
          "text": "The director felt that it wasn't \"shiny\" or \"happy\" - it made him look like a different person:",
          "image": "popup_images/crying_face.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 65000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "\"Spanky\" from The Little Rascals!",
          "image": "popup_images/spanky.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 70000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "The colors in the video are meant to be \"like a box of crayons.\"",
          "image": "popup_images/rabbit_hat.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_LEFT"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 75000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "The rest of the band was asked to wear \"their most colorful clothes\" to the shoot.",
          "image": "popup_images/fashion_dummy.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 82000,
          "durationMs": 5000,
          "text": "Kate designed her costume to be more than colorful - she has a specific look in mind:",
          "image": "popup_images/bra.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 88000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "A circus performer!",
          "image": "popup_images/circus.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 93000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "Kate was \"always in a good mood and full of energy\" on the day of the shoot.",
          "image": "popup_images/heart.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 99000,
          "durationMs": 4000,
          "text": "11 million people have been in a good mood since the introduction of Prozac in 1987.",
          "image": "popup_images/rising_chart.webp",
          "position": "BOTTOM_CENTER"
        },
        {
          "timeMs": 105000,
